(3, '{\"_method\":\"PUT\",\"title_es\":\"TECNO FIDTA, Exposici\\u00f3n Internacional de Tecnolog\\u00eda Alimentaria, Aditivos e Ingredientes\",\"title_en\":\"TECNO FIDTA, International Exhibition of Food Technology, Additives and Ingredients\",\"text_es\":\"<p>En el a&ntilde;o 2017 y como cada dos a&ntilde;os, tuvimos la oportunidad de participar de la Exposici&oacute;n Internacional de Tecnolog&iacute;a Alimentaria, Aditivos e Ingredientes. Realizada en el Centro Costa Salguero de Buenos Aires, Argentina.&nbsp;<br \\/>\\r\\nTecno Fidta se celebra cada dos a&ntilde;os en Buenos Aires y es uno de los eventos m&aacute;s importantes en el &aacute;mbito de la tecnolog&iacute;a alimentaria. Centrada especialmente en procesamiento; envasado y embotellado; aditivos; ingredientes y materias primas; refrigeraci&oacute;n; laboratorios y control de calidad; automatizaci&oacute;n y control; productos de higiene industrial; accesorios y perif&eacute;ricos, presenta los productos y servicios m&aacute;s innovadores.stros clientes.<\\/p>\",\"text_en\":\"<p>In the year 2017 and as every two years, we had the opportunity to participate in the International Exhibition of Food Technology, Additives and Ingredients. Held at the Costa Salguero Center in Buenos Aires, Argentina.<br \\/>\\r\\nTecno Fidta is celebrated every two years in Buenos Aires and is one of the most important events in the field of food technology. Focused especially on processing; packaging and bottling; additives; ingredients and raw materials; refrigeration; laboratories and quality control; automation and control; industrial hygiene products; accessories and peripherals, presents the most innovative products and services. its customers.<\\/p>\"}', '[{\"image\":\"gallery\\/noticia\\/iCDBmhDWdVZdxzS5KtTWf3KHTYRwRcY8qIHeKOH6.png\",\"title_es\":null,\"title_en\":null}]', 'aa', 2, '2019-06-27 18:45:10', '2019-06-27 20:38:29'),
