ero.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">PLC con Pantalla T&aacute;ctil para controlar las funciones b&aacute;sicas de la envasadora diagn&oacute;stico e informaci&oacute;n del estado de la misma.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Control electr&oacute;nico de ejes.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Foto correcci&oacute;n y largo de paquete controlados electr&oacute;nicamente.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">2 Motores de CA. de &frac34; HP con control electr&oacute;nico de velocidad y encoders.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Portabobinas simple auto centrado con freno.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Controladores de temperatura independientes para discos selladores y mordazas.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Mordazas rotativas de soldadura transversal.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Sistema de Doble mordaza standard. (FP-320)<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Sistema de Simple mordaza standard. (FP-500)<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Estaci&oacute;n de sellado transversal de doble apoyo regulable en altura.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Estaci&oacute;n de sellado longitudinal con dos pares de discos.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Dispositivo limitador de cupla en mordazas.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Parada de Mordaza en Fase<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Sistema de Fotocentrado de Impresi&oacute;n.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Molde conformador extensible y ajustable seg&uacute;n producto.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Puente de alimentaci&oacute;n de 2000 mm.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Mesa de salida de productos con banda de 500 mm.<\\/span><\\